                The system aims to modernize the food ordering process within office environments by providing:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>A responsive web interface for employees to browse menus and place orders</li>
                <li>Real-time order confirmation and delivery tracking features</li>
                <li>Role-based dashboards for employees, vendors, and administrators</li>
                <li>Efficient menu and order management</li>
                <li>Secure user authentication and payment history tracking</li>
                <li>Enhanced transparency and accountability to reduce food waste and improve service quality</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                Through this system, we aim to demonstrate our expertise in full-stack development using Microsoft’s ASP.NET Core ecosystem,
                along with strong UI/UX design, database integration, and role-based functionality.
            </p>
